At the “transactionItems” report a filter should be set up in a way that the F&amp;C module would report, only the first time they are captured, only ID’s belonging in the selected patterns of the included items Classes. An example of such a ReportSpec for the “urn:epc:pat:gid-96:145.233.{pre}*{/pre}” class is shown below.
