&lt;li&gt;BEA WebLogic. Understanding the Event, Master Data, and Data Exchange Services. BEA WebLogic RFID Entersprise Server. [Online] October 12, 2006. &lt;span class="nobr"&gt;&lt;a href="http://e-docs.bea.com/rfid/enterprise_server/docs20/pdf.html."&gt;&amp;#104;ttp://e-docs.bea.com/rfid/enterprise_server/docs20/pdf.html.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
